Jones to Make Record 101st Appearance for Wales Rugby vs England

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-08-04T12:14:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/jones-to-make-record-101st-appearance-for-wales-rugby-vs-england.html
Stephen Jones will make his record
101st appearance for the  Wales  rugby team when it meets England
at Twickenham Stadium in  London  in two days.  Jones will move one cap ahead of Gareth Thomas as Wales
plays its first warm-up match for the  World Cup , which begins
next month in New Zealand. Alun Wyn Jones will also make his
50th appearance, while Sam Warburton captains the team in place
of injured Matthew Rees.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  